  <span>Your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2021/08/twig-7/3d71cde8e5f23d28f9ce15dab441c4f2302d72a6.webm">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!</span>
</video></p>
</blockquote>


