<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@afranke:matrix.org">Alexandre Franke</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Busy week in Fractal land! It is the end for GSoC, but itâ€™s not really over. While some merge requests from our interns are still ongoing, Julian merged a bunch of them. On Kaiâ€™s side, the long awaited <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/fractal/-/merge_requests/789">Room details</a> are finally here. Alejandro, on the other hand, landed code to <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/fractal/-/merge_requests/802">get display name and avatar of accounts at startup</a>.</p>
